(10, 'Bala Box Office Collection Day 12: Ayushmann Khurrana Has 95 Crore Reasons To Smile', '<p><img src=\"https://c.ndtvimg.com/2019-11/7ebqm0j8_bala-instagram_625x300_20_November_19.jpg\" style=\"width: 650px;\"><i style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br></i></p><p><i style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Bala</i><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;Box Office: A still from the film.</span></p><div class=\"newins_widget marginb50 highlights_wrap\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 20px 20px 0px; float: left; width: 230px; padding: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; border-right: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238) !important;\"><div class=\"newins_widhead\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 209px; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">HIGHLIGHTS</h2></div><div class=\"newins_widmid\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 209px;\"><div class=\"lhs_highlights\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 209px; font-size: 13px;\"><ol style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 209px; counter-reset: item 0; padding: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.1em; list-style-type: inherit; display: block; line-height: 18px; margin-top: 0px !important; padding: 10px 0px !important; border-top: 0px !important;\">\"Bala is rock-steady,\" tweeted Taran Adarsh</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.1em; list-style-type: inherit; display: block; line-height: 18px; margin-top: 0px !important; padding: 10px 0px !important; border-top: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238) !important;\">Bala raked in&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;2 crore on Tuesday</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.1em; list-style-type: inherit; display: block; line-height: 18px; margin-top: 0px !important; padding: 10px 0px !important; border-top: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238) !important; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238) !important;\">Bala made&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;72 crore in its first week</li></ol></div></div><div class=\"newins_bottom\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; float: left; width: 209px;\"></div><div id=\"_pcwgtmid\" class=\"__pcwgtmid __pcwgtndtv fl\" data-wdgt=\"wgtlist=1&amp;wgtprice=on&amp;wgtsplrlogo=on&amp;wgtoffertext=on&amp;wgtthumbimg=on\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); display: inline; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Ayushmann Khurrana\"s new film&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/bala-box-office-collection-day-11-ayushmann-khurranas-film-is-slow-and-steady-with-rs-92-crore-2134939\" target=\"_self\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(50, 104, 145) !important;\">inching closer to the&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;100 crore mark with each passing day</a>. The Bollywood comedy, which is currently in its second week in theatres, continues to charm the audiences and increase its box office numbers in turn. In 12 days, Ayushmann\"s&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;has recorded a score of&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;95 crore, reported trade analyst Taran Adarsh. On its second week,&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;made&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;3.76 crore on Friday,&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;6.73 crore on Saturday,&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;8 crore on Sunday,&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;2.25 crore on Monday and&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;2.05 on Tuesday. In his tweet, he wrote: \"<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;is rock-steady... [Week 2] Fri 3.76 cr, Sat 6.73 cr, Sun 8.01 cr, Mon 2.25 cr, Tue 2.05 cr. Total:&nbsp;<span class=\"rupee\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: RupeeForadianRegular !important;\">R<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; left: -9999em; position: absolute; text-indent: -9999em;\">s.</span></span>&nbsp;95.04 cr. India biz.\"</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Take a look at&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>\"s box office report here:</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">In its first week,&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;made a score of Rs 72 crore, when Mr Adarsh wrote: \"<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;is fantastic.\"&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" style=\"width: 272px;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">On its release day,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/bala-box-office-collection-day-1-ayushmann-khurranas-film-has-excellent-opening-day-with-rs-10-15-cr-2129826\" target=\"_self\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(50, 104, 145) !important;\"><i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;had an excellent opening with Rs 10 crore</a>, when Taran Adarsh said: \"Strong word of mouth plus brand Ayushmann are key contributors.\"</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>&nbsp;was welcomed with positive reviews both by audiences and critics alike. Ayushmann Khurrana stars as a young protagonist dealing with premature balding while Bhumi Pednekar and Yami Gautam feature in supporting roles. Ayushmann, who added one more hit film to his impressive resume with&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Bala</i>, recently told news agency IANS: \"It feels amazing that my films are being loved by audiences across the country. I believe this box office run is a responsibility given to me to do better work and provide better entertainment to the people of my country.\"<br></p>', 'movie', '2019-11-20', 'Entertainment');
