ical-align: baseline; width: 600px; max-width: 100%;\">Classes are kept small, with about eight students in a session, and the students are paired with volunteer dance instructors. “We have a mix of skills and abilities,” Ms. Elbogen said. “That’s not unusual for most ballet classes. The students are learning classical ballet, gaining confidence, improving their motor and verbal skills, and having fun.”</p></div></div></section>', 'int', '2019-11-20', 'National');
